2007-01-08  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@gnome.org>

	* gnome-dialog.c: (gnome_dialog_get_type):
	* gnome-druid.c: (gnome_druid_accessible_get_type),
	(gnome_druid_accessible_factory_get_type):
	* gnome-entry.c: (gnome_entry_get_type):
	* gnome-file-entry.c: (gnome_file_entry_get_type):
	* gnome-ui-init.c: (libgnomeui_set_property):
	Don't make all the GTypeInfo stuff static. Reduces
	relocations. Patch from Christian Persch. Closes
	bug #360628.

