	* gnome-authentication-manager.c: (vfs_async_question_callback),
	(vfs_question_callback): Patch to make the dialog thread safe.
	Patch from (jylefort@FreeBSD.org). Closes bug #312180.

2006-02-07  Kjartan Maraas  <kmaraas@gnome.org>

	* gnome-entry.c: (gnome_entry_class_init):
	* gnome-icon-entry.c: (ientry_browse):
	Reuse some existing strings to cut down on redundancy.
	Reported by Clytie Siddall. Closes bug #314767.

