2002-04-22  Anders Carlsson  <andersca@gnu.org>

	* gnome-icon-entry.c: Use our own delete_event handler for the dialog
	so that it won't get destroyed. Fixes #75230.

Fri Apr 19 21:02:09 2002  George Lebl <jirka@5z.com>

	* gnome-about.c: Fix #77931, that is, open only one credits dialog.
	  when one is already open just gtk_window_present the dialog.

Fri Apr 19 16:25:18 2002  George Lebl <jirka@5z.com>

	* gnome-file-entry.c, gnome-icon-entry.c: export the file expanding
	  function from file-entry to icon-entry (underscore prefixed
	  function not in a header) and use this in icon entry so that
	  we can store our selection outside of the file entry which changes
	  often.  This way we fix #76640 and #77215.  Fix a few leaks
	  in icon entry.  Use gtk_window_present to show the dialog once
	  hidden.  Always reselect the picked icon on the dialog to have
	  proper 'Cancel' behaviour.

