	optionmenu after populating it to workaround bug #66969
	(day_selected): gtk_calendar_get_date() already returns month in
	the 0-11 range
	(select_clicked): gtk_calendar_select_month() expects month to be
	in the 0-11 range, while g_date_get_month() is 1-12.

