Sun Dec 09 14:15:01 2001  George Lebl <jirka@5z.com>

	* gnome-dialog.c, gnome-messagebox.c: Contrary to popular belief,
	  va_list is not a pointer and certainly not a string vector.  Use
	  the constructv method in the messagebox and don't check for
	  nullness of va_list in gnome_dialog_construct.

