	* Makefile.am: Install the schema file.

	* libgnomeui.schemas: Add a scheme entry
	for show-icons, hopefully resulting with this defaulting
	to on.

	* gnome-app.c (gnome_app_instance_init): Ref/sink 
	app->layout.

