	* gnome-client.[ch], gnome-ui-init.c: require the gnome-client module
	  and update it for the new way of doing gnome modules

	* gnome-gconf-ui.[ch], libgnomeui.h:  make the header private and
	  use the new module init stuff.

	* gnome-ui-init.[ch]: do the getter style module stuff, and remove
	  bonoboui stuff which is empty anyway.  Make the old style
	  init stuff deprecated and add gnome_init macro, and put in
	  docs from 1.0 for those.

	* libgnomeui.h: remove the COMPAT_1_0 bit at the bottom, that's quite
	  bogus

	* libgnomeuiP.h: add gnome-gconf-ui.h here

